casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Peggy M. HAIRSTON ROBINSON.
No. D-3022.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 2, 2018.
Peggy M. Hairston Robinson, of Baton Rouge, Louisiana, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and rule a will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
